(text "== USB-C power inputs: three CH224K PD sink triggers ==" (at 20.32 12.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 350a3986-1d35-5ca2-8a33-e9bef4f7f7c0))
(text "Each CH224K uses resistor mode: CFG1=56k to GND requests 15V; CFG2/CFG3 are NC." (at 20.32 20.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a4ca6be5-af4b-51f3-8168-eb0afce00765))
(text "CH224K performs USB-C PD negotiation; BQ25798 on sheet 1 is the buck-boost charger / NVDC power path." (at 20.32 27.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a5577deb-95b0-5849-9c8c-db49afb856dc))
(text "Only J21 carries USB2 D+/D- to BQ25798; J22/J23 are power-only charge inputs." (at 20.32 35.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid d84e5f54-f678-5404-aae9-5dcfcbf1426a))
(text "== J21 USB-C PD sink input 1: CH224K requests 15V ==" (at 20.32 50.8 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 2951f5b3-6127-5420-8266-a74c026e31a2))
